gate: OPEN
task: S76-TA1
title: Locale JSON Completion — en/ru/uk All Namespaces
description: |
  Add all missing translation keys to src/locales/en.json, ru.json, uk.json.
  No component code changes in this task — data only.

  PATCH ru.json + uk.json (keys exist in en.json but MISSING in ru/uk):
    login.signingIn / login.otpRequired
    objects.* (entire namespace — title, search, noVehicles, selectTitle)

  ADD to all 3 files (new namespaces, used by TB–TG tasks):

  common (extend):
    apply / retry / saveChanges / enabled / disabled / active / noDescription / goBack / search

  reports (extend):
    reportType, period, periodWhole, periodDaily, company, vehicles,
    noneSelected, vehiclesSelected, buildReport, vehicleSelection, noType,
    noReports, report_label, from, to, downloading,
    status.queued / status.error / status.cancelled / status.completed / status.building,
    errors.loadFailed / errors.deleteFailed / errors.deleted / errors.downloadFailed

  objectDetails (new):
    title, tabs.history, tabs.events, noData,
    errors.loadFailed, errors.historyFailed

  events (new — maps to EVENTS_CONFIG ids):
    speeding, outGeofence, stop, geofenceIn, geofenceOut,
    fuelDischarge, fuelCharge, sos, ignitionOn, ignitionOff, powerOff, powerOn

  tracking (new):
    title, actionTitle, selectVehicles, vehicle, selectVehiclePlaceholder,
    timeInterval, events, eventsCount, trackDisplay, color, width,
    execute, unknownVehicle, errors.dateRange,
    analytics.maxSpeed, analytics.avgSpeed, analytics.stops, analytics.fuelEff

  accountSecurity (new):
    title, region, email, emailLinked, thirdPartyVoice, changePassword,
    faceId, patternLock, multiDevice, twoFactor, twoFactorSub,
    userCode, deleteAccount, outOfSync, notSet, statusOff,
    assignEmail, emailPlaceholder, saveChanges,
    errors.emailRequired, errors.emailSaved, errors.emailFailed,
    errors.fieldsRequired, errors.passwordMismatch, errors.passwordSaved, errors.passwordFailed

  twoFactor (new):
    title, subtitle, googleAuth, googleAuthSub, enabled, disabled,
    howItWorks, step1, step2, step3,
    errors.toggleFailed

  engine (new):
    title, notAvailable, noPermission, notEquipped, goBack,
    statusUnOPEN, statusOPEN, connectionInfo,
    lockSafe, emergencyBlock, unlock,
    confirm.lock, confirm.emergency, confirm.emergencyFinal, confirm.unlock,
    errors.checkFailed,
    success.OPEN, success.emergencyOPEN, success.unOPEN, errors.actionFailed

  settings (extend):
    loading, retry

  drivers (new):
    search, empty, confirmDelete, deleted, deleteFailed, loadFailed, createNotImpl

  geozones (new):
    search, empty, noDescription, confirmDelete, deleted, deleteFailed, loadFailed, createNotImpl

  maintenance (new):
    search, empty, confirmDelete, removed, removeFailed, loadFailed, createNotImpl,
    tabs.templates, tabs.journal

  See S76-TRANSLATIONS-REFERENCE.md (optional companion) for full en/ru/uk string values.

acceptance:
  - All 3 locale files contain identical key sets (no missing keys)
  - ru.json and uk.json have no English fallback strings in the new namespaces
  - tsc --noEmit exits 0 (no type errors from changed locale structure)

requires: [FRONTEND_DEV]
estimated: 3 hours
